  "description": "<i>Escape</i> is a point &amp; click adventure game set in a prison cell block. You are an inmate, and your goal is to escape the prison. You can move freely between cells and talk to other inmates, as well as visit other rooms in the prison like the medical office.<br><br>The scene is shown in third-person perspective, and across the bottom of the screen is a row of inventory items. Left-clicking on an object or character is used to describe it, and right-clicking performs an action, such as talking to another inmate. During conversation, the options for what you can choose to say are shown in a purple block at the top of the screen.",
